  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Start the day with a hot and cold buffet breakfast.</p>
<p>Your evening meal is also buffet style, so you can sample delicious local and international dishes. There is a selection of Slovenian wines on the menu to complement your meal (payable locally). </p>
<p>Sustainability is important throughout the hotel and the kitchen is no exception. Slovenian and international dishes are made with fresh, locally-sourced produce, and served buffet style - to minimise food waste, you're encouraged to take several small plates rather than one large plate - you can go back to the buffet several times if you want.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
