  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Rooms in the main hotel</strong></p>
<p><strong>Double Rooms </strong>sleep two people with an Austrian Twin bed. Some rooms are available with a single sofa bed so can sleep three (please note that if the room is booked just for two people there won't be a sofa-bed). </p>
<p><strong>Double Rooms with balcony </strong>sleep two people with an Austrian Twin bed. Some rooms are available with a single sofa bed so can sleep three (please note that if the room is booked just for two people there won't be a sofa-bed). </p>
<p><strong>Family Rooms </strong>sleep four people with an Austrian Twin bed and additional double sofa bed.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms in the main hotel have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Air-conditioning</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Bath or shower</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Luxury Glamping Pods </strong>are located in a separate area of the hotel grounds (around 50 metres from the main hotel building) that has a natural swimming pool only accessible by guests in the glamping pods. The glamping pods sleep four people with a double bed on the lower floor and an additional double bed on the mezzanine (accessed by ladder). Glamping pods have a private hot-tub on the terrace, and a infrared sauna. The ensuite has a bath or shower, and there's a TV, mini fridge and hairdryer in each pod. </p>
<p><strong>General information</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Check-in: <strong>2pm</strong></li>
<li>Check-out: <strong>11am</strong></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Local fees and taxes</strong></p>
<p>A resort tourist tax of approx. €3.13 per adult per night is payable locally. Children aged 12-17 years pay a discounted rate of approx. €1.56 per night, and children aged 11 and under are exempt.</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>
<p>Only the main hotel building has a lift. For the glamping pods, each pod is accessed by around seven steps from the ground to the terrace and entrance.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
